Definition: a word that denotes one thing but refers to a related thing
Example: Washington is a metonym for the United States government; plastic is a metonym for credit card
Synonyms: adj, all, figurative, metonymic, metonymical, word, a, that, denotes, one, thing, but, refers, to, related, Washington, is, for, the, United, States, government, plastic, credit, card
Category: noun.communication
